WEBVTT

00:00:00.096 --> 00:01:00.096

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
[Episode 01]

00:01:34.510 --> 00:01:35.680
(Even years later, )

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:38.280
(I still see this
mountain path in my dreams.)

00:01:38.710 --> 00:01:41.560
(Winding away like
a mystery I'll never solve.)

00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:44.200
(One end reaching out to the world, )

00:01:44.590 --> 00:01:47.126
(and the other vanishing into the mist.)

00:01:47.150 --> 00:01:48.286
This is steep.

00:01:48.310 --> 00:01:49.550
A truck would never make it up.

00:01:53.070 --> 00:01:54.070
Wanzhi.

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:55.280
We're in a distant village.

00:01:55.350 --> 00:01:56.470
Why'd you have to tag along?

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:58.560
The second she heard we were coming,

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:00.480
she couldn't sleep a wink.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:01.640
She just had to come.

00:02:02.230 --> 00:02:03.870
You just love a challenge, don't you?

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:05.120
Here, Fang.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:06.000
Let me carry her.

00:02:06.070 --> 00:02:07.070
I'm fine, really.

00:02:09.190 --> 00:02:10.360
My dear principal.

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.400
Madam County Magistrate.

00:02:11.470 --> 00:02:12.800
Your health isn't great.

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:14.080
Don't push yourself.

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:16.070
Well, I'm the one who had her.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:17.560
As a mother,

00:02:17.870 --> 00:02:19.520
this is just what we do for our kids.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.750
(That village nestled in the clouds)

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.630
(has a lovely name.)

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.480
(It's called Shenxian Peak.)

00:02:34.150 --> 00:02:35.150
Name?

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.150
Yang Sanjin.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.280
You got sick?

00:02:37.630 --> 00:02:38.630
I'm not sick.

00:02:39.710 --> 00:02:40.710
She is.

00:02:41.470 --> 00:02:43.000
I asked for the patient's name.

00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:44.750
He Xiaoqin.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.000
My wife.

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:46.960
Listen, family member,

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.000
please wait outside.

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:51.440
It's a gynecological exam.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:53.240
It's better if family stays out there.

00:02:56.430 --> 00:02:57.030
Doctor.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.680
Give her a good, thorough checkup.

00:02:58.910 --> 00:02:59.976
See if she can

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:01.000
still give me a son.

00:03:02.520 --> 00:03:03.520
Please, step out.

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:08.360
Your name is He Xiaoqin?

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:18.680
He Xiaoqin?

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:20.080
Look at me.

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.686
That man who was just in here,

00:03:25.710 --> 00:03:26.750
is he really your husband?

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:31.976
The injuries on your body,

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.000
where did they come from?

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:37.400
Were you trafficked to this place?

00:03:38.280 --> 00:03:39.280
Don't be afraid.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.286
I can call the police

00:03:40.310 --> 00:03:41.030
and get you help.

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:42.400
I wasn't trafficked!

00:03:43.470 --> 00:03:44.670
My father and grandfather were

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:46.320
both born and raised here.

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:48.190
My parents live just up the hill.

00:03:49.710 --> 00:03:51.240
Then when your husband was in here,

00:03:51.630 --> 00:03:52.750
why wouldn't you look at me?

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:54.560
I

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.430
I was looking at her.

00:04:03.030 --> 00:04:04.030
Age?

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:05.120
Twenty-seven.

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.360
Principal Fang.

00:04:06.430 --> 00:04:07.496
Mr. Li needs you for a consult.

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:08.080
It's urgent.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.030
Okay.

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:10.150
He Xiaoqin.

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:11.240
Wait for me here.

00:04:19.270 --> 00:04:20.310
Why are you staring at me?

00:04:20.870 --> 00:04:21.870
Because you're beautiful.

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:25.630
You know.

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:27.750
I once had a little sister.

00:04:29.630 --> 00:04:30.950
If she were still with us today,

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.800
she'd be about your age.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.240
Could I...

00:04:37.950 --> 00:04:39.270
Could I touch your face?

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:53.360
Stay away from my mom!

00:04:53.430 --> 00:04:54.430
She's sick!

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:59.000
You brat!

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:00.720
How can you say your own mother is sick?

00:05:00.870 --> 00:05:01.870
She really is!

00:05:02.070 --> 00:05:03.000
If she scratches you,

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:04.640
my family can't afford the medical bill!

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:05.600
Who's asking for your money?

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:06.950
This is my mom's medical tent.

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:08.600
Get out! Get out of here!

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:14.680
Lady.

00:05:14.870 --> 00:05:15.480
Go ahead.

00:05:15.830 --> 00:05:18.240
I... I'm sick.

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:19.600
I'm not scared.

00:05:37.830 --> 00:05:38.990
Why do you keep following me?

00:05:42.830 --> 00:05:44.310
Does your mom only scratch kids?

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:45.190
No.

00:05:45.510 --> 00:05:46.720
She scratches my dad the most,

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:47.680
pretty violently.

00:05:47.950 --> 00:05:49.630
Sometimes we even have to tie her up.

00:05:50.360 --> 00:05:51.310
Tying up your own mother?

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.510
You're a real piece of work.

00:05:52.950 --> 00:05:54.360
My dad and I didn't want to.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.640
The doctor told us we had to.

00:05:59.270 --> 00:06:00.830
Is there anything fun to do here?

00:06:01.950 --> 00:06:04.430
How about I take you to see the gods?

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:05.720
Stop lying.

00:06:06.040 --> 00:06:08.070
There are no gods on Shenxian Peak.

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:09.190
Only hardworking farmers.

00:06:09.270 --> 00:06:10.270
My mom already told me.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:11.920
Fine.

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:13.480
We'll catch mudfish.

00:06:14.600 --> 00:06:15.760
Look! There's one over there!

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:16.600
Where?

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:17.270
Let me see!

00:06:17.310 --> 00:06:17.830
Right there!

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.240
Take me there!

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:21.680
Hurry!

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:22.720
Where is it?

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.000
There's one here.

00:06:24.720 --> 00:06:25.630
Look over there!

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.576
A big one right there!

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:27.600
Where?

00:06:27.630 --> 00:06:28.310
In front of you.

00:06:28.630 --> 00:06:29.920
No, a little closer to me.

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:32.240
Grab it!

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:33.800
God!

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:34.720
Look!

00:06:34.830 --> 00:06:35.830
See? The god is here!

00:06:38.750 --> 00:06:39.750
Silly.

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:41.310
That is a paratrooper.

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:44.270
Hello, Mr. Paratrooper!

00:06:44.830 --> 00:06:46.560
Hello, Mr. Paratrooper!

00:06:46.750 --> 00:06:47.750
Come on, hurry!

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:49.120
Let's go see him!

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.480
Run!

00:07:12.430 --> 00:07:13.920
Whose girl are you?

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:16.270
What are you doing in my field?

00:07:18.630 --> 00:07:19.310
Grandpa!

00:07:19.430 --> 00:07:20.430
They're coming!

00:07:20.510 --> 00:07:21.166
They're here again!

00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:22.190
Let's go!

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.680
Move aside!

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:38.920
Make way, please.

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:39.830
Move back, everyone.

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:41.040
Give us some room.

00:07:42.750 --> 00:07:44.950
This is just a routine exercise.

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:45.537
Keep it stable.

00:07:45.561 --> 00:07:46.720
The plane hit some strong

00:07:47.190 --> 00:07:48.800
turbulence at high altitude.

00:07:49.430 --> 00:07:50.190
This comrade here

00:07:50.270 --> 00:07:51.630
was the last one to jump,

00:07:51.950 --> 00:07:52.480
and luckily,

00:07:52.830 --> 00:07:54.390
he drifted right into our village.

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:55.600
It just goes to show

00:07:55.750 --> 00:07:57.630
what great luck Shenxian Peak has.

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:59.120
Don't you all agree?

00:07:59.240 --> 00:08:00.800
Yes! You're right!

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:03.096
The man who saved my daughter,

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:04.120
how is he?

00:08:04.510 --> 00:08:05.920
His wounds have been treated.

00:08:06.070 --> 00:08:07.390
But it's a pretty serious injury.

00:08:08.390 --> 00:08:09.430
What's his name?

00:08:20.270 --> 00:08:21.510
Hello, Comrade He Yongwang.

00:08:21.950 --> 00:08:23.910
I'm Fang Jingyu from
the Yu County Nursing School.

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:24.750
Just now,

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.360
it was my daughter you saved.

00:08:26.830 --> 00:08:28.120
You were injured because of her.

00:08:28.430 --> 00:08:29.630
I'd like to make it up to you,

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:31.600
but first, thank you so much.

00:08:32.630 --> 00:08:33.630
Oh, no, don't say that.

00:08:33.870 --> 00:08:35.750
It really wasn't such a big deal.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:37.200
It's...

00:08:41.790 --> 00:08:42.790
It's you!

00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:47.150
Stop right there!

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:55.720
What are we gonna do?

00:08:55.790 --> 00:08:56.767
She's in so much pain!

00:08:56.791 --> 00:08:58.006
Why aren't you helping her?

00:08:58.030 --> 00:08:59.110
Get her to a hospital, now!

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:00.910
I know she's hurting!

00:09:02.120 --> 00:09:03.480
What can we do?

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.670
My wife's in labor!

00:09:05.910 --> 00:09:07.200
Can anyone help us?

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:08.870
You'll see once you get to the hospital!

00:09:08.910 --> 00:09:09.910
What are we going to do?

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:11.000
What's going on?

00:09:11.080 --> 00:09:12.270
This woman's giving birth!

00:09:12.550 --> 00:09:13.630
How old is she?

00:09:13.670 --> 00:09:14.246
She's 40.

00:09:14.270 --> 00:09:15.246
Has she had children before?

00:09:15.270 --> 00:09:15.870
She's had two.

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.630
One's 19, and the other's 17.

00:09:17.870 --> 00:09:18.870
Both are girls.

00:09:19.790 --> 00:09:20.750
No time for the hospital.

00:09:20.790 --> 00:09:21.870
Take her to my house first.

00:09:22.670 --> 00:09:23.670
Don't just stand there!

00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:24.440
She's the most

00:09:24.510 --> 00:09:26.056
famous obstetrician in all of Yu County.

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:26.790
Guys, give us a hand.

00:09:26.870 --> 00:09:27.600
Help us carry her.

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:28.870
Sure thing! On it!

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:38.000
You really are lucky.

00:09:38.030 --> 00:09:39.030
The baby was transverse.

00:09:39.150 --> 00:09:40.630
If you hadn't run into Director Fang,

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.150
it would have been a C-section.

00:09:42.510 --> 00:09:43.510
Thank you so much!

00:09:43.720 --> 00:09:44.840
Is it a boy or a girl?

00:09:49.360 --> 00:09:50.360
Sir.

00:09:51.270 --> 00:09:52.750
This child is absolutely beautiful.

00:09:53.150 --> 00:09:54.270
Congratulations!

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:55.840
Mother and daughter are both safe.

00:09:58.150 --> 00:09:59.360
Go on, hold your little girl.

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:15.320
Grandma Yu.

00:10:15.510 --> 00:10:16.830
The tricycle at the door is gone.

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:17.750
Where is that couple?

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:19.670
They snuck off first thing this morning.

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:21.126
I saw they weren't holding the baby,

00:10:21.150 --> 00:10:22.150
so I chased.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.057
But these old legs of mine

00:10:23.081 --> 00:10:24.361
were no match for that tricycle.

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:26.080
So the child,

00:10:26.630 --> 00:10:27.360
she was abandoned?

00:10:27.630 --> 00:10:28.630
Exactly.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:33.720
I'm so sorry.

00:10:34.120 --> 00:10:35.150
I'm a monster.

00:10:35.870 --> 00:10:36.870
I'm truly guilty!

00:10:37.030 --> 00:10:38.270
I'm not even human!

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:40.270
I shouldn't have done that!

00:10:41.510 --> 00:10:42.510
He Yongwang!

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:43.720
You're a father!

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:45.600
Where on earth is your conscience?

00:10:45.750 --> 00:10:46.750
I'm sorry.

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:48.360
Save your breath.

00:10:49.670 --> 00:10:51.200
Just... just hit me!

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:53.280
If it makes you feel better, hit me!

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:54.320
Go ahead!

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:00.000
If you won't do it,

00:11:00.670 --> 00:11:01.790
then I'll do it myself!

00:11:02.750 --> 00:11:03.750
I'm a monster!

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:05.120
I'm a monster!

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:06.360
I'm so sorry!

00:11:06.670 --> 00:11:07.670
I'm so sorry!

00:11:07.870 --> 00:11:08.870
I'm so sorry!

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:09.750
Forgive me!

00:11:09.870 --> 00:11:10.870
Mom?

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:46.600
Mom.

00:11:48.120 --> 00:11:49.550
That man saved my life.

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:51.846
So why is he kneeling there,

00:11:51.870 --> 00:11:53.080
slapping his own face?

00:11:56.270 --> 00:11:57.870
It's just some grown-up business,

00:11:58.510 --> 00:11:59.550
it doesn't concern you.

00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:03.670
As for Shenxian Peak,

00:12:04.360 --> 00:12:05.360
I only hope

00:12:05.390 --> 00:12:06.390
that from now on,

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.920
you'll never have to look back at it.

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:29.240
She's out as soon as
she closes her eyes.

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:35.870
What's on your mind?

00:12:39.150 --> 00:12:40.510
I wanted to tell her the truth,

00:12:41.270 --> 00:12:42.126
but I just didn't know

00:12:42.150 --> 00:12:43.150
how to find the words.

00:12:44.030 --> 00:12:45.030
That man promised

00:12:45.750 --> 00:12:46.607
he'd never come back

00:12:46.631 --> 00:12:47.750
to trouble us or the child.

00:12:54.200 --> 00:12:55.270
I've let you down.

00:12:56.150 --> 00:12:57.480
Taking care of Wanzhi,

00:12:58.240 --> 00:12:59.720
I missed my chance to conceive.

00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:02.216
I couldn't give you

00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:03.360
a child of our own.

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:05.360
What are you talking about?

00:13:09.510 --> 00:13:11.056
The first word she ever spoke

00:13:11.080 --> 00:13:11.750
was "Daddy".

00:13:12.030 --> 00:13:14.320
Besides, I'm the one

00:13:14.750 --> 00:13:16.200
who named her Wanzhi.

00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:18.487
Doesn't that make her

00:13:18.511 --> 00:13:19.550
our very own child?

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:22.727
Maybe we should talk to

00:13:22.751 --> 00:13:23.840
the local police station,

00:13:24.270 --> 00:13:25.910
and change Wanzhi's surname to Meng.

00:13:26.840 --> 00:13:27.840
But why?

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:29.670
When we first registered her,

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:30.886
you said she'd take my name.

00:13:30.910 --> 00:13:31.950
I didn't think much of it.

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:34.320
But she's starting school soon.

00:13:34.670 --> 00:13:35.960
A Deputy Magistrate's daughter

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:37.200
taking her mother's name

00:13:37.750 --> 00:13:38.750
it's just a bit unusual.

00:13:39.030 --> 00:13:40.320
What's unusual about it?

00:13:40.870 --> 00:13:42.670
You're the one who delivered her,

00:13:42.790 --> 00:13:44.150
right here in our own home.

00:13:44.600 --> 00:13:46.270
She was always meant to be yours.

00:13:46.510 --> 00:13:47.510
And look,

00:13:47.630 --> 00:13:48.766
the Fang family has given

00:13:48.790 --> 00:13:50.080
so much to Yu County.

00:13:50.720 --> 00:13:52.000
Now with Wanzhi,

00:13:52.870 --> 00:13:54.360
the legacy can finally continue.

00:13:55.270 --> 00:13:56.270
It's perfect.

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:02.550
Clouds for rain, and wind for snow.

00:14:03.080 --> 00:14:04.960
Sunsets against the clearing sky.

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:07.240
Returning geese, and swallows low.

00:14:07.910 --> 00:14:09.790
Resting birds, and crickets' cry.

00:14:10.630 --> 00:14:13.240
A 3-foot blade, a 6-stone bow...

00:14:16.670 --> 00:14:17.670
North...

00:14:18.030 --> 00:14:19.310
North of the ridge, to the flow.

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:19.960
Good!

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:22.150
That's enough for today.

00:14:22.360 --> 00:14:23.360
How's that?

00:14:23.630 --> 00:14:24.630
Come here, sweetie.

00:14:24.790 --> 00:14:25.790
Okay!

00:14:29.550 --> 00:14:30.390
These are so complex.

00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:31.240
Can you write them?

00:14:31.440 --> 00:14:32.440
Of course I can.

00:14:32.670 --> 00:14:33.600
Daddy says

00:14:33.670 --> 00:14:35.190
it's how you build a solid foundation.

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:37.480
Keep it up!

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:38.200
I will.

00:14:38.360 --> 00:14:39.360
Go on, then.

00:14:41.320 --> 00:14:41.847
Next semester,

00:14:41.871 --> 00:14:43.550
I'm gunning to be the art class rep.

00:14:43.670 --> 00:14:44.200
How about you?

00:14:44.440 --> 00:14:45.440
I want to be one, too.

00:14:45.630 --> 00:14:46.630
Then go for it.

00:14:46.670 --> 00:14:47.176
See ya!

00:14:47.200 --> 00:14:48.200
Bye-bye!

00:14:50.910 --> 00:14:51.910
Stop shouting!

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:53.080
I said stop it!

00:14:56.910 --> 00:14:58.030
Stop it!

00:15:02.390 --> 00:15:03.600
Mind your own business.

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:07.246
We're not at school right now.

00:15:07.270 --> 00:15:08.790
Think that badge gives you power here?

00:15:09.000 --> 00:15:10.080
You're in Class 301, right?

00:15:10.270 --> 00:15:11.296
I just saw.

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:12.550
Mrs. Liu doing home visits

00:15:12.790 --> 00:15:13.790
around the corner.

00:15:13.840 --> 00:15:14.840
Just you wait!

00:15:15.790 --> 00:15:16.790
Let's get out of here!

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:29.440
Are you okay?

00:15:32.240 --> 00:15:32.910
She was bluffing!

00:15:33.200 --> 00:15:34.200
Better start running!

00:15:34.750 --> 00:15:35.750
Run!

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:38.000
Grandma Yu!

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:40.006
Grandma Yu!

00:15:40.030 --> 00:15:41.030
What's wrong, Wanzhi?

00:15:41.960 --> 00:15:42.960
What happened?

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:45.600
What's going on here?

00:15:46.150 --> 00:15:47.150
Come on.

00:15:58.360 --> 00:15:59.360
Turn around.

00:16:01.390 --> 00:16:02.720
You're in Class 201, right?

00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:04.080
Why were you fighting them?

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:05.720
They were making fun of me.

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:07.080
Making fun of what?

00:16:07.150 --> 00:16:07.960
My name.

00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:09.150
And what is your name?

00:16:09.270 --> 00:16:10.150
Li Yudan. [♪Fishegg]

00:16:10.270 --> 00:16:11.270
How is it written?

00:16:11.360 --> 00:16:12.150
"Yu" for fish,

00:16:12.240 --> 00:16:13.240
and "Dan" for egg.

00:16:13.320 --> 00:16:14.646
Why on earth did they name you that?

00:16:14.670 --> 00:16:15.750
My mom sells fish,

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:16.870
and my dad sold eggs.

00:16:18.960 --> 00:16:20.480
I guess "Yudan"

00:16:20.600 --> 00:16:21.960
is fine for a nickname.

00:16:22.270 --> 00:16:23.720
But now that you're in school,

00:16:23.870 --> 00:16:25.510
it really does make you a target.

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:26.630
Tell you what.

00:16:26.790 --> 00:16:27.846
Go home and ask your dad

00:16:27.870 --> 00:16:28.870
to change it for you.

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:32.550
My dad's dead. Car crash.

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:34.006
Then ask your mother

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:35.030
to change it.

00:16:35.200 --> 00:16:36.480
My mom can't read or write.

00:16:37.550 --> 00:16:38.670
Then I'll change it for you.

00:16:42.670 --> 00:16:44.080
The next two lines

00:16:44.120 --> 00:16:45.510
are my favorites.

00:16:46.510 --> 00:16:47.790
Frost upon the wayfarer's brow,

00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:49.960
wandering in the early light.

00:16:51.000 --> 00:16:52.200
Mist upon the fisher's cloak,

00:16:52.840 --> 00:16:54.360
casting lines into the night.

00:16:57.790 --> 00:16:58.790
Li...

00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:05.830
Li Xingke. [♪Wayfarer]

00:17:05.960 --> 00:17:06.480
Yes.

00:17:06.510 --> 00:17:07.510
Li Xingke.

00:17:12.030 --> 00:17:13.030
How are the ribs?

00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:14.880
They're okay. A bit of a kick.

00:17:15.400 --> 00:17:16.400
Thanks.

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:18.510
Go easy on the chili next time.

00:17:19.440 --> 00:17:20.440
Is anyone home?

00:17:21.510 --> 00:17:22.510
I'll get it.

00:17:25.640 --> 00:17:26.640
Hello? Anyone there?

00:17:29.310 --> 00:17:30.310
Yes, hello.

00:17:30.830 --> 00:17:31.830
Who are you looking for?

00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:33.710
I'm looking for Fang Wanzhi.

00:17:34.030 --> 00:17:35.030
She's my daughter.

00:17:35.680 --> 00:17:37.000
Is there something wrong?

00:17:40.200 --> 00:17:41.087
Did she get into trouble?

00:17:41.111 --> 00:17:42.440
Did she hurt your son?

00:17:42.960 --> 00:17:43.550
Oh, no!

00:17:43.790 --> 00:17:44.456
My son was being

00:17:44.480 --> 00:17:45.480
bullied by some bad kids.

00:17:45.550 --> 00:17:46.550
Your daughter saved him.

00:17:46.790 --> 00:17:48.000
She even bandaged his wounds.

00:17:52.310 --> 00:17:54.000
So, you're Wanzhi?

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:55.240
Yes, I am.

00:17:56.000 --> 00:17:57.000
Thank you so much!

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:58.720
Come on, son. Give her a bow.

00:17:59.920 --> 00:18:00.920
There's no need.

00:18:02.590 --> 00:18:03.240
These are fish heads

00:18:03.400 --> 00:18:04.030
and some parts.

00:18:04.110 --> 00:18:05.110
I've cleaned them all up.

00:18:05.240 --> 00:18:05.566
Take them.

00:18:05.590 --> 00:18:06.086
No, no.

00:18:06.110 --> 00:18:07.110
We can't take them.

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:08.527
The name Wanzhi gave

00:18:08.551 --> 00:18:09.680
my son is just beautiful.

00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:10.726
Anyway, you'd have to pay

00:18:10.750 --> 00:18:11.726
a scholar for that.

00:18:11.750 --> 00:18:12.160
Please.

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:13.217
Really, regardless,

00:18:13.241 --> 00:18:14.400
we shouldn't take anything.

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:17.200
What?

00:18:17.400 --> 00:18:18.440
Think it's not worth much?

00:18:18.680 --> 00:18:19.550
Well, toss it in the bin

00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:20.640
once we've left then.

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:22.200
Oh, that's not what I meant.

00:18:24.030 --> 00:18:24.680
Alright, alright.

00:18:25.030 --> 00:18:26.720
I'll take them then.

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:27.640
Here.

00:18:27.830 --> 00:18:28.830
Thank you.

00:18:29.070 --> 00:18:30.590
I could tell you were an intellectual.

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:31.720
You're too kind.

00:18:33.720 --> 00:18:35.160
Would you like to come in for a bit?

00:18:35.640 --> 00:18:36.200
No.

00:18:36.440 --> 00:18:37.440
We won't trouble you.

00:18:37.510 --> 00:18:38.110
We'll be off.

00:18:38.440 --> 00:18:39.440
Alright then, take care.

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:40.750
Goodbye!

00:18:40.830 --> 00:18:42.240
Xingke?

00:18:43.680 --> 00:18:44.680
Actually quite clever.

00:18:45.240 --> 00:18:46.087
The name you picked

00:18:46.111 --> 00:18:47.400
is better than the one I had.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:49.246
I was actually planning

00:18:49.270 --> 00:18:50.510
to call him "Diaowen". [Angler]

00:18:50.680 --> 00:18:51.680
But then,

00:18:51.750 --> 00:18:53.136
I thought it sounded like an old man.

00:18:53.160 --> 00:18:54.200
Yeah, totally!

00:18:58.240 --> 00:18:59.320
You're a brave little girl,

00:18:59.750 --> 00:19:00.750
you know that?

00:19:01.510 --> 00:19:02.510
Brave,

00:19:03.200 --> 00:19:04.590
and always ready to help others.

00:19:05.110 --> 00:19:06.110
Right?

00:19:06.640 --> 00:19:07.640
Just like your mom.

00:19:10.590 --> 00:19:13.150
Back when I was sick,
(Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org)

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:15.070
Nobody had the guts to treat me.

00:19:15.750 --> 00:19:16.766
If your mom hadn't happened

00:19:16.790 --> 00:19:17.790
to pass through there,

00:19:17.960 --> 00:19:19.790
I would've died in that cowshed.

00:19:24.830 --> 00:19:25.830
Daddy?

00:19:25.920 --> 00:19:27.440
What kind of sickness did you have?

00:19:27.550 --> 00:19:29.270
Why was everyone too scared to help?

00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:35.270
It was a matter of history.

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:37.510
You'll understand when you're older.

00:19:50.440 --> 00:19:51.440
Come out!

00:19:56.110 --> 00:19:57.110
Why are you following me?

00:19:57.680 --> 00:19:59.680
Can I do my homework at your place?

00:20:00.510 --> 00:20:01.510
My mom said

00:20:01.750 --> 00:20:02.750
from now on,

00:20:02.790 --> 00:20:04.350
she'll bring your family fish each day.

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:05.880
No way. My dad said

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:07.350
we can't take things from people.

00:20:08.270 --> 00:20:09.920
Where did you use to do your homework?

00:20:10.830 --> 00:20:11.830
At the market.

00:20:12.110 --> 00:20:13.310
But when my mom scales fish,

00:20:13.790 --> 00:20:15.440
it always spatters all over my notebooks.

00:20:15.880 --> 00:20:17.920
She says you're a great student,

00:20:18.270 --> 00:20:20.270
and if I follow you,
I'll make something of myself.

00:20:20.400 --> 00:20:21.400
Still no.

00:20:22.240 --> 00:20:23.240
Unless...

00:20:23.310 --> 00:20:23.960
Unless what?

00:20:24.200 --> 00:20:25.400
Unless you call me big sister.

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:29.400
I'm eight and you're seven.

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:30.600
It isn't exactly a raw deal.

00:20:31.030 --> 00:20:31.696
Do it, or you're not

00:20:31.720 --> 00:20:32.720
coming over to my house.

00:20:35.750 --> 00:20:37.110
Big sister!

00:20:45.070 --> 00:20:45.680
Take a break.

00:20:45.920 --> 00:20:46.960
Have some cake first.

00:20:48.350 --> 00:20:49.350
Go on.

00:20:50.350 --> 00:20:51.590
It's fine, eat up.

00:20:54.350 --> 00:20:55.350
What is it?

00:20:55.400 --> 00:20:56.790
Do you really need her permission?

00:20:57.440 --> 00:20:58.440
I'm the one offering it.

00:20:58.550 --> 00:20:59.550
Don't be shy.

00:21:01.400 --> 00:21:02.400
Thank you, ma'am.

00:21:03.070 --> 00:21:04.070
Wait a second.

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:06.440
Wash your hands first.

00:21:13.510 --> 00:21:15.240
Come on! Go, go, go!

00:21:15.270 --> 00:21:15.830
She dodged it!

00:21:16.030 --> 00:21:17.896
Go for it! Get her!

00:21:17.920 --> 00:21:18.480
Come on!

00:21:18.790 --> 00:21:19.287
Get over here!

00:21:19.311 --> 00:21:21.976
Faster! Faster!

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:23.000
Missed it! Missed it!

00:21:23.110 --> 00:21:25.030
Go, go, go!

00:21:25.640 --> 00:21:28.960
Keep going! Almost there!

00:21:31.640 --> 00:21:32.640
What is it?

00:21:33.350 --> 00:21:34.350
Why the long face?

00:21:36.550 --> 00:21:38.440
For a child from a family like ours,

00:21:39.110 --> 00:21:40.000
should she really...

00:21:40.030 --> 00:21:40.617
Should she really

00:21:40.641 --> 00:21:41.790
play with kids like that?

00:21:42.400 --> 00:21:43.400
I know, right?

00:21:43.550 --> 00:21:45.160
Wanzhi's classmate, Hu Tongyu,

00:21:45.480 --> 00:21:47.070
her father is the County Magistrate.

00:21:47.480 --> 00:21:48.720
Her mother told me

00:21:49.000 --> 00:21:50.840
that since you're
the Nursing School Principal,

00:21:51.270 --> 00:21:52.720
you're a senior official now.

00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:54.216
She wants Wanzhi

00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:55.750
to be friends with her daughter.

00:21:56.350 --> 00:21:57.440
She said those other kids

00:21:57.590 --> 00:21:59.160
just aren't in our league.

00:21:59.350 --> 00:22:01.270
What's this talk about leagues?

00:22:01.750 --> 00:22:02.750
They're so young.

00:22:02.960 --> 00:22:04.270
Cut the social stratification.

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:06.550
I think what Wanzhi is doing

00:22:06.750 --> 00:22:07.350
is wonderful.

00:22:07.480 --> 00:22:08.480
Don't you think so?

00:22:10.110 --> 00:22:10.880
Wanzhi!

00:22:11.030 --> 00:22:12.160
Dinnertime!

00:22:14.070 --> 00:22:14.750
Missed again!

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:15.880
Wanzhi!

00:22:17.310 --> 00:22:18.310
Who did this?

00:22:21.270 --> 00:22:22.270
Small as you are,

00:22:22.440 --> 00:22:23.440
you've got quite a throw!

00:22:29.830 --> 00:22:32.030
I... I'm sorry, sir.

00:22:32.550 --> 00:22:33.590
It's me.

00:22:34.270 --> 00:22:35.440
Li Xingke, is it?

00:22:36.920 --> 00:22:37.920
Been meaning to ask you.

00:22:38.590 --> 00:22:39.696
In Chapter 27 of the Three Kingdoms,

00:22:39.720 --> 00:22:40.440
what happens?

00:22:40.720 --> 00:22:42.520
The Lord of the Magnificent
Beard rides alone,

00:22:42.550 --> 00:22:44.150
and the Hanshou Lord slays six generals.

00:22:44.920 --> 00:22:45.920
So that's you!

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:47.440
Now, listen closely.

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:49.246
When you're reading my books,

00:22:49.270 --> 00:22:50.270
wash your hands first.

00:22:50.310 --> 00:22:51.486
If you can't finish, that's fine,

00:22:51.510 --> 00:22:52.200
but no dog-ears.

00:22:52.480 --> 00:22:53.480
Learn to use a bookmark.

00:22:53.920 --> 00:22:54.550
Got it?

00:22:54.880 --> 00:22:55.880
Got it.

00:22:56.000 --> 00:22:56.440
Good.

00:22:56.550 --> 00:22:57.550
Off you go then.

00:22:59.750 --> 00:23:00.750
Time to eat.

00:23:01.550 --> 00:23:02.070
Dad?

00:23:02.350 --> 00:23:03.880
Can he join us for dinner?

00:23:04.310 --> 00:23:05.590
His mom is out picking up stock.

00:23:08.920 --> 00:23:10.200
He calls you big sister, right?

00:23:10.880 --> 00:23:12.376
When a brother eats
at his sister's house,

00:23:12.400 --> 00:23:13.440
he doesn't need an excuse.

00:23:14.030 --> 00:23:15.030
Thanks, Dad!

00:23:20.510 --> 00:23:21.510
Principal Fang!

00:23:23.750 --> 00:23:24.830
What a coincidence!

00:23:25.070 --> 00:23:26.070
It's no coincidence.

00:23:26.550 --> 00:23:28.030
I came here to bring you some fish.

00:23:29.110 --> 00:23:30.216
You shouldn't keep doing this.

00:23:30.240 --> 00:23:30.937
Siyuan has already

00:23:30.961 --> 00:23:32.350
scolded me several times about it.

00:23:32.750 --> 00:23:33.830
But it's Saturday!

00:23:33.880 --> 00:23:34.550
The kids are back.

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:36.270
This is the freshest sturgeon.

00:23:36.510 --> 00:23:38.000
Make sure Wanzhi gets a taste.

00:23:38.200 --> 00:23:38.790
Alright, then.

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.480
But I insist on paying you this time.

00:23:41.200 --> 00:23:42.590
Oh, no, please!

00:23:42.960 --> 00:23:43.960
When my silly son

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:45.030
first met Wanzhi,

00:23:45.270 --> 00:23:45.936
we had no idea

00:23:45.960 --> 00:23:46.720
between you two,

00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:47.680
one is a Principal

00:23:47.880 --> 00:23:49.080
and the other is a Magistrate!

00:23:49.240 --> 00:23:50.047
If we'd known,

00:23:50.071 --> 00:23:51.351
we never would've aimed so high.

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:52.550
I mean, people must be

00:23:52.720 --> 00:23:53.920
lining up to bring you gifts!

00:23:55.270 --> 00:23:56.880
But this... this isn't a bribe.

00:23:57.110 --> 00:23:58.470
It's just a token of my gratitude.

00:23:58.960 --> 00:24:00.000
If it weren't for Wanzhi,

00:24:00.200 --> 00:24:01.200
do you think my silly boy

00:24:01.720 --> 00:24:02.376
would've made it into

00:24:02.400 --> 00:24:03.400
the elite middle school?

00:24:03.720 --> 00:24:04.830
A few fish are nothing!

00:24:05.070 --> 00:24:06.350
I'd gladly give her

00:24:06.550 --> 00:24:07.550
a lifetime supply.

00:24:08.350 --> 00:24:09.350
Here, take it.

00:24:29.030 --> 00:24:30.200
What are you doing over here?

00:24:30.440 --> 00:24:31.480
Why didn't you come to me?

00:24:33.880 --> 00:24:34.766
Why are you

00:24:34.790 --> 00:24:35.790
so brooding today?

00:24:36.590 --> 00:24:37.590
You've got puppy love?

00:24:37.920 --> 00:24:38.920
I don't.

00:24:41.110 --> 00:24:42.110
Your face?

00:24:42.270 --> 00:24:43.270
Let me see.

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:44.920
Turn around!

00:24:47.480 --> 00:24:48.480
Who did this?

00:24:48.920 --> 00:24:50.320
Was it those same three guys again?

00:24:54.270 --> 00:24:54.830
Listen.

00:24:55.160 --> 00:24:56.200
Tomorrow at 2:00 PM,

00:24:56.790 --> 00:24:57.616
tell everyone from Yu

00:24:57.640 --> 00:24:58.680
who's studying in Jianglin

00:24:58.920 --> 00:24:59.920
to come over to my home.

00:25:01.750 --> 00:25:02.910
Should I tell the girls, too?

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:04.030
Of course!

00:25:04.400 --> 00:25:05.400
I'll handle the girls.

00:25:05.510 --> 00:25:06.510
You handle the boys.

00:25:08.310 --> 00:25:10.000
This fish is so fresh!

00:25:10.590 --> 00:25:11.160
Wanzhi,

00:25:11.590 --> 00:25:12.590
eat up.

00:25:20.110 --> 00:25:20.640
Dad.

00:25:20.880 --> 00:25:21.616
You're heading down to

00:25:21.640 --> 00:25:22.760
the villages again tomorrow?

00:25:23.440 --> 00:25:24.030
What of it?

00:25:24.440 --> 00:25:25.047
Complaining about

00:25:25.071 --> 00:25:26.160
me working every weekend?

00:25:27.110 --> 00:25:27.920
Oh, not at all!

00:25:28.110 --> 00:25:29.110
Work always comes first.

00:25:32.480 --> 00:25:33.480
Mom.

00:25:33.550 --> 00:25:34.550
Why don't you take.

00:25:34.960 --> 00:25:36.480
Grandma Yu out shopping tomorrow?

00:25:36.880 --> 00:25:37.960
Maybe buy some new clothes.

00:25:38.480 --> 00:25:39.720
I have everything I need.

00:25:39.790 --> 00:25:40.790
Why go shopping?

00:25:41.720 --> 00:25:43.400
She wants to host a party again

00:25:43.880 --> 00:25:45.320
and wants us to give her some space.

00:25:49.790 --> 00:25:50.920
Besides Xingke,

00:25:51.720 --> 00:25:53.510
who else has been
shaken down by those three?

00:25:56.880 --> 00:25:57.880
I have.

00:25:58.160 --> 00:25:59.160
Last Monday,

00:25:59.440 --> 00:26:01.000
they stole 14 yuan from me.

00:26:01.750 --> 00:26:02.750
I've been robbed, too.

00:26:03.440 --> 00:26:04.440
Twice.

00:26:05.750 --> 00:26:06.750
Wanzhi,

00:26:06.920 --> 00:26:08.040
they've cornered us as well.

00:26:08.550 --> 00:26:09.750
Luckily we were together,

00:26:10.830 --> 00:26:11.830
otherwise...

00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:17.830
My grandpa fought off bandits at 16.

00:26:18.590 --> 00:26:20.350
We people from Yu County
don't pick fights,

00:26:22.200 --> 00:26:23.840
but we won't let anyone walk all over us!

00:26:26.310 --> 00:26:27.310
What's this?

00:26:29.550 --> 00:26:30.550
What do you want?

00:26:31.440 --> 00:26:32.327
Those girls behind us

00:26:32.351 --> 00:26:33.440
seem to be following us.

00:26:34.030 --> 00:26:35.270
Maybe they have a crush on you?

00:26:35.680 --> 00:26:36.350
Get lost.

00:26:36.440 --> 00:26:38.030
Too bad they're not much to look at.

00:26:59.830 --> 00:27:00.830
What do you want?

00:27:01.070 --> 00:27:02.070
Get out of the way.

00:27:02.400 --> 00:27:03.400
Move it!

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:06.310
You mugged us.

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:09.480
Oh, it's you.

00:27:10.550 --> 00:27:11.550
Look at you now,

00:27:12.920 --> 00:27:14.000
even bringing girls along.

00:27:16.680 --> 00:27:17.960
Listen up, everyone!

00:27:18.310 --> 00:27:19.310
Get lost right now!

00:27:19.640 --> 00:27:21.240
I'll wreck whoever is too slow to leave!

00:27:30.110 --> 00:27:31.350
Which one of you is the leader?

00:27:31.590 --> 00:27:32.590
Do you even have one?

00:27:33.110 --> 00:27:34.110
Come out and fight me.

00:27:34.350 --> 00:27:35.480
You want a fight?

00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:38.480
How do you want to do this?

00:27:40.440 --> 00:27:41.440
Get a guy out here.

00:27:42.510 --> 00:27:43.656
If word gets out I beat up a girl,

00:27:43.680 --> 00:27:44.680
it'll be embarrassing.

00:27:44.920 --> 00:27:45.550
Don't point at me!

00:27:45.790 --> 00:27:46.790
Afraid of a girl?

00:27:46.880 --> 00:27:47.920
You're fighting me.

00:27:49.750 --> 00:27:50.750
Fang Wanzhi.

00:27:50.960 --> 00:27:52.320
I know your dad is a big official.

00:27:52.680 --> 00:27:53.800
The "Princess of Yu County."

00:27:53.830 --> 00:27:54.486
Can't mess with you.

00:27:54.510 --> 00:27:55.400
I'll just leave, alright?

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:56.640
Think you can just walk away?

00:27:56.880 --> 00:27:57.880
What do you want then?

00:27:59.440 --> 00:28:00.760
You guys mug people all the time,

00:28:01.160 --> 00:28:02.360
I bet you're carrying weapons.

00:28:02.480 --> 00:28:03.480
We outnumber you,

00:28:03.790 --> 00:28:04.767
yet you can still

00:28:04.791 --> 00:28:05.960
win the fight.

00:28:06.310 --> 00:28:07.510
But once the police arrive,

00:28:07.830 --> 00:28:09.400
it'll be assault with a deadly weapon.

00:28:09.510 --> 00:28:11.150
You'll be expelled from school, at least.

00:28:11.350 --> 00:28:12.590
And whether you go to detention

00:28:13.200 --> 00:28:14.376
depends on all the other

00:28:14.400 --> 00:28:15.640
crap you've pulled before.

00:28:16.920 --> 00:28:17.920
Fang Wanzhi.

00:28:18.310 --> 00:28:19.390
A man doesn't fight a girl.

00:28:20.240 --> 00:28:21.176
We won't cross each other,

00:28:21.200 --> 00:28:21.720
okay?

00:28:21.790 --> 00:28:22.790
Not okay.

00:28:22.830 --> 00:28:23.976
You think because you're locals,

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:25.240
you can bully us outsiders?

00:28:25.920 --> 00:28:26.976
Assaulting us, stealing money,

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:28.070
and harassing girls...

00:28:28.680 --> 00:28:29.680
It won't be that easy.

00:28:30.750 --> 00:28:31.750
What then?

00:28:32.400 --> 00:28:33.440
You want to slap me?

00:28:35.110 --> 00:28:36.110
I'll...

00:28:39.920 --> 00:28:40.657
Give yourselves

00:28:40.681 --> 00:28:41.801
three slaps across the face.

00:28:41.880 --> 00:28:42.880
Apologize to everyone,

00:28:43.400 --> 00:28:44.087
and promise never to

00:28:44.111 --> 00:28:45.286
mug anyone from Yu County again.

00:28:45.310 --> 00:28:46.310
Then I'll let you go.

00:28:47.400 --> 00:28:49.680
Otherwise, start saying your last words.

00:28:52.240 --> 00:28:53.240
I'll watch myself now.

00:28:53.550 --> 00:28:54.830
I'll stay far away from you all.

00:28:59.030 --> 00:28:59.640
I'm sorry!

00:28:59.830 --> 00:29:00.830
Forgive me!

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:02.680
Let those two go.

00:29:06.310 --> 00:29:07.590
Girls, step back.

00:29:07.750 --> 00:29:08.750
Boys, get him!

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:11.976
Wait, wait, wait!

00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:13.000
I give up! I surrender!

00:29:13.880 --> 00:29:14.880
I never thought

00:29:14.920 --> 00:29:15.456
the Princess

00:29:15.480 --> 00:29:16.480
would school me.

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:17.880
Fang Wanzhi,

00:29:18.240 --> 00:29:19.240
I had a crush on you.

00:29:19.350 --> 00:29:20.720
Don't make me slap myself.

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:22.216
You can hit me once, I'll take it.

00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:22.856
Give me dignity,

00:29:22.880 --> 00:29:23.880
okay?

00:29:24.510 --> 00:29:25.440
Have a crush on my sister?

00:29:25.510 --> 00:29:26.160
In your dreams!

00:29:26.400 --> 00:29:26.880
Get him!

00:29:26.920 --> 00:29:28.400
No! Wait! Stop!

00:29:28.680 --> 00:29:29.680
Stop hitting me!

00:29:30.400 --> 00:29:31.400
Cut it out!

00:29:31.680 --> 00:29:32.270
I give up!

00:29:32.510 --> 00:29:33.510
Ouch!

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:36.160
Grandma Yu!

00:29:36.400 --> 00:29:37.400
I'm home!

00:29:43.750 --> 00:29:45.000
Mom, I'm home.

00:29:45.920 --> 00:29:46.920
Wanzhi's back!

00:29:47.000 --> 00:29:47.976
Wanzhi's back!

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:49.000
Well, Ms. Fang,

00:29:49.310 --> 00:29:50.550
we'll be heading out now.

00:29:50.640 --> 00:29:51.640
I won't see you out.

00:29:52.200 --> 00:29:52.616
Alright.

00:29:52.640 --> 00:29:53.216
Take care.

00:29:53.240 --> 00:29:53.750
Let's go.

00:29:54.160 --> 00:29:55.480
Take care, everyone! Bye!

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:01.310
Mom.

00:30:01.440 --> 00:30:02.440
Stand up straight!

00:30:04.030 --> 00:30:05.270
You've really outdone yourself.

00:30:08.590 --> 00:30:10.270
Stood up for them,
and they snitched on me?

00:30:10.720 --> 00:30:11.720
Some friends they are!

00:30:12.200 --> 00:30:13.200
Nobody snitched on you.

00:30:14.350 --> 00:30:15.007
Those women

00:30:15.031 --> 00:30:16.110
came here to thank me.

00:30:17.200 --> 00:30:18.200
To thank my daughter,

00:30:18.640 --> 00:30:19.640
who rallied all the

00:30:19.680 --> 00:30:20.726
kids from Yu County together,

00:30:20.750 --> 00:30:22.240
punished those little bullies,

00:30:22.510 --> 00:30:23.680
and emerged victorious!

00:30:24.480 --> 00:30:25.720
What a hero you are!

00:30:26.830 --> 00:30:27.830
It was nothing.

00:30:28.110 --> 00:30:29.880
I couldn't exactly
embarrass my mom, could I?

00:30:30.350 --> 00:30:31.790
You sound awfully proud of yourself.

00:30:34.160 --> 00:30:34.920
What's this.

00:30:35.030 --> 00:30:36.030
"Princess of Yu County"?

00:30:37.310 --> 00:30:38.590
It's just some silly nickname.

00:30:39.270 --> 00:30:40.006
If you weren't always

00:30:40.030 --> 00:30:41.110
bragging about your father,

00:30:41.240 --> 00:30:42.790
would people even know who you are?

00:30:45.590 --> 00:30:46.590
I... I don't

00:30:46.640 --> 00:30:48.200
exactly brag about it all the time.

00:30:48.510 --> 00:30:49.640
Fighting is one thing,

00:30:50.350 --> 00:30:51.950
but letting people call you a "princess"

00:30:52.030 --> 00:30:53.590
is an even bigger failure on your part!

00:30:54.030 --> 00:30:55.070
Relying on your parents,

00:30:55.200 --> 00:30:55.857
do you really think

00:30:55.881 --> 00:30:57.441
that's how you'll make it in the world?

00:30:58.310 --> 00:30:59.310
If you keep this up,

00:30:59.550 --> 00:31:00.327
you'll become the kind

00:31:00.351 --> 00:31:01.590
I despise the most!

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:32.000
Your grandpa used to say

00:31:32.680 --> 00:31:33.680
that we live three fates.

00:31:34.590 --> 00:31:35.790
The first is given by parents.

00:31:36.510 --> 00:31:37.456
It determines the family

00:31:37.480 --> 00:31:38.480
you're born into

00:31:38.720 --> 00:31:39.790
and the genes you carry.

00:31:40.830 --> 00:31:41.990
This is called Heavenly Fate.

00:31:42.830 --> 00:31:43.936
The second is defined by

00:31:43.960 --> 00:31:45.790
your own experiences and choices.

00:31:46.550 --> 00:31:47.550
It's called Real Fate.

00:31:48.640 --> 00:31:50.160
The third is bestowed by education.

00:31:51.070 --> 00:31:52.150
It's called Self-made Fate.

00:31:52.720 --> 00:31:54.680
There are so many people today,

00:31:55.400 --> 00:31:56.720
especially children of officials,

00:31:57.200 --> 00:31:59.240
who brag about status and Heavenly Fate.

00:32:00.310 --> 00:32:02.110
It's the most pathetic, toxic trend.

00:32:02.680 --> 00:32:03.840
Those truly worthy of respect

00:32:04.590 --> 00:32:06.550
are those who prove their value through

00:32:07.310 --> 00:32:08.750
their Real Fate and Self-made Fate.

00:32:12.440 --> 00:32:14.270
Mom, I'll remember that.

00:32:15.510 --> 00:32:16.510
Come here.

00:32:21.270 --> 00:32:22.590
Read this word for me.

00:32:26.240 --> 00:32:27.480
Vanity.

00:32:28.640 --> 00:32:30.310
Your grandpa was a legend in Yu County.

00:32:31.440 --> 00:32:32.440
When I was little,

00:32:32.920 --> 00:32:34.440
I went through the same thing you did.

00:32:35.550 --> 00:32:36.550
As a result,

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:38.310
I was forced to write

00:32:38.350 --> 00:32:39.750
that word 10,000 times.

00:32:40.960 --> 00:32:42.030
Now, it's your turn.

00:32:42.550 --> 00:32:44.110
If you truly believe you were wrong,

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:48.960
you'll fill every one of these pages.

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:52.480
(Back then, )

00:32:52.750 --> 00:32:54.750
(I couldn't wrap
my head around her fury.)

00:32:55.750 --> 00:32:56.960
(Later, she told me)

00:32:57.510 --> 00:32:59.350
(that life is about more
than just surviving.)

00:32:59.830 --> 00:33:03.110
(It's about the moral choices we make.)

00:33:04.240 --> 00:33:06.880
(Some are born with a less
than ideal Heavenly Fate, )

00:33:07.350 --> 00:33:11.240
(but earn respect through their
Real Fate and Self-made Fate.)

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:13.240
(I asked her, )

00:33:13.640 --> 00:33:15.560
("What if I'm destined
for a life of obscurity?")

00:33:16.400 --> 00:33:17.590
(She whispered, )

00:33:18.440 --> 00:33:19.790
("Then you must work even harder)

00:33:20.310 --> 00:33:21.590
(to simply be a good person.")

00:33:22.310 --> 00:33:23.640
("An ordinary, good person)

00:33:24.440 --> 00:33:27.750
(is still one tiny light among billions.")

00:33:32.750 --> 00:33:34.880
(Next up, it's performance time!)

00:33:35.070 --> 00:33:36.920
(Please welcome our host, Han Bin!)

00:33:37.590 --> 00:33:38.590
(Han Bin!)

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:39.640
(Han Bin is here!)

00:33:40.270 --> 00:33:41.270
(Hello, everyone!)

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:42.480
(I'm Han Bin.)

00:33:43.030 --> 00:33:44.750
(I'd like to share an essay with you.)

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:46.680
(Vanity in the Autumn Wind.)

00:33:47.350 --> 00:33:49.070
(By Anonymous.)

00:33:49.960 --> 00:33:52.110
(The autumn wind in
Yu County is gentle.)

00:33:52.880 --> 00:33:54.376
(Basking in the brilliant, )

00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:55.750
(dazzling sunlight of autumn, )

00:33:56.400 --> 00:33:57.880
(nature's colors are painted)

00:33:58.440 --> 00:34:00.240
- Wanzhi!
- (with a profound sense of depth.)

00:34:00.880 --> 00:34:01.350
Wanzhi.

00:34:01.790 --> 00:34:03.046
You wrote this article yourself.

00:34:03.070 --> 00:34:04.070
Why didn't you sign?

00:34:04.550 --> 00:34:05.550
Listen to the rest.

00:34:06.350 --> 00:34:07.680
(In my memory, )

00:34:08.710 --> 00:34:11.280
(autumn in Yu County is
the most beautiful.)

00:34:12.000 --> 00:34:13.150
(That autumn, )

00:34:13.710 --> 00:34:14.646
(I was 15.)

00:34:14.670 --> 00:34:15.607
What a beautiful voice.

00:34:15.631 --> 00:34:17.231
(I'd already left my home in Yu County.)

00:34:17.800 --> 00:34:18.800
Thanks, Mom.

00:34:19.280 --> 00:34:20.280
Love you, too.

00:34:22.070 --> 00:34:23.070
Dad?

00:34:24.070 --> 00:34:25.670
He hasn't called me yet.

00:34:26.510 --> 00:34:27.087
But I bet

00:34:27.111 --> 00:34:28.480
he'll call any minute now.

00:34:28.670 --> 00:34:30.230
No matter how busy Vice Mayor Meng is,

00:34:30.510 --> 00:34:31.510
he wouldn't forget

00:34:31.670 --> 00:34:32.670
my birthday, right?

00:34:35.670 --> 00:34:37.000
Okay, don't worry, Mom.

00:34:37.880 --> 00:34:38.960
Give my best to Grandma Yu.

00:34:40.510 --> 00:34:41.510
Gotta go.

00:34:47.280 --> 00:34:48.280
Ma'am,

00:34:48.360 --> 00:34:49.630
is there still no call for me?

00:34:49.960 --> 00:34:50.960
No.

00:34:52.960 --> 00:34:53.590
Hello.

00:34:53.920 --> 00:34:55.550
Could you put me through to Meng Siyuan?

00:34:56.190 --> 00:34:57.190
I'm his daughter.

00:35:00.480 --> 00:35:01.480
He's not in?

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:04.440
Alright then.

00:35:12.710 --> 00:35:13.360
Wanzhi!

00:35:13.670 --> 00:35:14.840
We're all set.

00:35:15.110 --> 00:35:16.360
Are you done with your parents?

00:35:18.320 --> 00:35:19.000
Yeah, all done.

00:35:19.070 --> 00:35:19.480
Let's go!

00:35:19.590 --> 00:35:20.590
Let's go!

00:35:32.710 --> 00:35:33.840
Sorry, Wanzhi.

00:35:34.190 --> 00:35:35.280
I'm late.

00:35:35.550 --> 00:35:36.840
You're the only one who's late.

00:35:37.000 --> 00:35:38.160
You'll finish a whole bottle.

00:35:38.360 --> 00:35:39.360
Deal.

00:35:40.000 --> 00:35:41.120
Look at you, all dressed up.

00:35:44.590 --> 00:35:45.590
Light the candles!

00:35:50.510 --> 00:35:51.510
Ready.

00:35:52.230 --> 00:35:55.190
Happy birthday to you!

00:35:55.480 --> 00:35:58.360
Happy birthday to you!

00:35:58.840 --> 00:36:02.150
Happy birthday, dear Wanzhi!

00:36:02.670 --> 00:36:05.920
Happy birthday to you!

00:36:08.190 --> 00:36:09.190
Wanzhi.

00:36:09.400 --> 00:36:10.510
What did you wish for?

00:36:11.590 --> 00:36:12.590
Take a guess.

00:36:13.440 --> 00:36:14.440
Still playing games?

00:36:15.150 --> 00:36:17.000
From the look on your face,

00:36:17.150 --> 00:36:18.270
I bet you asked for romance.

00:36:21.230 --> 00:36:22.320
You nailed it.

00:36:25.110 --> 00:36:26.840
I'm pretty happy with
everything right now.

00:36:27.400 --> 00:36:28.337
The only thing missing

00:36:28.361 --> 00:36:29.480
in my life is a boyfriend.

00:36:30.030 --> 00:36:30.856
I've never been

00:36:30.880 --> 00:36:31.880
in a relationship.

00:36:32.030 --> 00:36:33.310
I'm truly looking forward to it.

00:36:37.710 --> 00:36:38.360
Xingke.

00:36:38.630 --> 00:36:39.166
You were late.

00:36:39.190 --> 00:36:39.736
Were you busy

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:40.760
getting me a gift?

00:36:43.400 --> 00:36:44.400
Let's see it then.

00:36:46.320 --> 00:36:47.280
Sorry, Wanzhi.

00:36:47.320 --> 00:36:49.030
I actually didn't have time to get one.

00:36:49.630 --> 00:36:50.630
I'll make it up to you.

00:36:52.150 --> 00:36:53.550
Who cares about your gifts anyway?

00:36:55.960 --> 00:36:56.880
You're 20 now.

00:36:56.920 --> 00:36:58.080
It's time you started dating.

00:36:58.230 --> 00:36:59.630
Time to find yourself a girlfriend.

00:37:34.150 --> 00:37:35.150
Wait!

00:37:40.550 --> 00:37:41.550
Thanks.

00:37:48.840 --> 00:37:49.920
It's overloaded.

00:38:06.670 --> 00:38:08.320
Please welcome Han Bin,

00:38:08.550 --> 00:38:09.630
our school magazine editor

00:38:09.670 --> 00:38:10.950
and contest judge, to the stage!

00:38:11.480 --> 00:38:13.320
His outfit is so on point today.

00:38:13.440 --> 00:38:14.560
I'm totally crushing on him.

00:38:17.960 --> 00:38:18.960
No speech prepared.

00:38:19.190 --> 00:38:20.190
As a judge,

00:38:20.360 --> 00:38:21.960
I'd just like to highlight one essay and

00:38:22.510 --> 00:38:23.510
share my thoughts on it.

00:38:24.590 --> 00:38:25.800
The title of the piece is.

00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:28.440
Four Seasons in a Small Town.

00:38:28.670 --> 00:38:30.110
My review of this essay

00:38:30.510 --> 00:38:31.760
consists of just 11 words.

00:38:32.230 --> 00:38:33.550
"The quality is pure as jade,

00:38:33.960 --> 00:38:35.670
a true masterpiece of jade."

00:38:36.550 --> 00:38:37.127
This is the best

00:38:37.151 --> 00:38:38.230
essay I've read

00:38:38.510 --> 00:38:40.030
since joining the editorial board.

00:38:40.150 --> 00:38:41.150
Bar none.

00:38:45.630 --> 00:38:46.630
Han Bin.

00:38:51.590 --> 00:38:52.590
Fang Wanzhi.

00:38:54.150 --> 00:38:55.150
Congrats on the win.

00:38:55.760 --> 00:38:56.760
Thank you.

00:38:58.030 --> 00:38:59.230
Actually, I wanted to say

00:38:59.480 --> 00:39:01.006
if you had entered with your other piece,

00:39:01.030 --> 00:39:02.110
Vanity in the Autumn Wind,

00:39:02.400 --> 00:39:03.880
you would've had an even better shot.

00:39:05.840 --> 00:39:07.360
And don't tell me you didn't write it.

00:39:09.150 --> 00:39:10.550
But I didn't even sign my name.

00:39:10.920 --> 00:39:12.040
How could you possibly know?

00:39:12.590 --> 00:39:13.630
I was the one who read it

00:39:13.670 --> 00:39:14.670
for the school broadcast.

00:39:15.150 --> 00:39:16.166
The whole school was guessing

00:39:16.190 --> 00:39:17.190
who the author could be.

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:18.920
I was curious, too.

00:39:19.230 --> 00:39:20.710
But once I read.

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:22.190
Four Seasons in a Small Town,

00:39:22.480 --> 00:39:24.080
I knew instantly it was the same person.

00:39:25.230 --> 00:39:26.127
If I didn't even have

00:39:26.151 --> 00:39:27.190
that much discernment,

00:39:27.510 --> 00:39:29.030
I'd be a pretty lousy judge.

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:30.600
You're something, you know that?

00:39:31.030 --> 00:39:32.030
You're too kind.

00:39:33.150 --> 00:39:34.150
Yu County

00:39:34.510 --> 00:39:36.550
it sounds so beautiful in your writing.

00:39:37.030 --> 00:39:38.126
It's so vivid that I'm

00:39:38.150 --> 00:39:39.230
dying to see it for myself.

00:39:40.320 --> 00:39:41.320
When I do,

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:42.630
would you be my guide?

00:39:43.230 --> 00:39:44.230
It would be an honor.

00:40:06.550 --> 00:40:07.550
What a coincidence!

00:40:09.030 --> 00:40:10.030
Yeah, it is.

00:40:12.440 --> 00:40:13.606
You two are so full of it.

00:40:13.630 --> 00:40:14.630
Coincidence? Please.

00:40:15.670 --> 00:40:16.567
I saw someone

00:40:16.591 --> 00:40:17.800
looking around earlier.

00:40:18.110 --> 00:40:19.350
Weren't you looking for Wanzhi?

00:40:24.320 --> 00:40:25.400
I'm done. Bye!

00:40:37.070 --> 00:40:38.070
Here, have a drumstick.

00:40:39.110 --> 00:40:40.110
Thanks.

00:40:50.030 --> 00:40:51.030
Wanzhi.

00:40:51.070 --> 00:40:52.070
Let me tell you,

00:40:52.110 --> 00:40:53.880
Han Bin is a total legend.

00:40:54.110 --> 00:40:56.510
He writes, he's great at reciting,

00:40:56.630 --> 00:40:57.550
plays the guitar,

00:40:57.630 --> 00:40:58.630
and he's an athlete!

00:40:59.320 --> 00:41:00.047
Plus, his father

00:41:00.071 --> 00:41:01.190
is a provincial big shot.

00:41:01.360 --> 00:41:02.336
He's a literal.

00:41:02.360 --> 00:41:03.360
Prince Charming.

00:41:03.840 --> 00:41:04.670
He's clearly into you.

00:41:04.710 --> 00:41:05.910
Don't let this chance slip by!

00:41:06.110 --> 00:41:07.230
He is not into me.

00:41:07.590 --> 00:41:08.416
We just sat together

00:41:08.440 --> 00:41:09.440
for a quick meal.

00:41:27.590 --> 00:41:28.630
Running all by yourself?

00:41:30.320 --> 00:41:31.640
I guess you got no boyfriend yet.

00:41:31.960 --> 00:41:32.960
I'm a local.

00:41:33.110 --> 00:41:34.350
I know every inch of this city.

00:41:34.630 --> 00:41:35.630
How about a ride?

00:41:37.440 --> 00:41:38.070
I'll pass.

00:41:38.110 --> 00:41:39.550
I've heard motorcycles aren't safe.

00:41:40.110 --> 00:41:41.280
And I don't have a helmet.

00:41:46.190 --> 00:41:46.710
It's brand new.

00:41:47.190 --> 00:41:48.190
I got it for you.

00:41:48.550 --> 00:41:49.710
Try it on and see if it fits.

00:42:38.150 --> 00:42:38.800
What do you think?

00:42:39.000 --> 00:42:39.896
This is the best buffet

00:42:39.920 --> 00:42:40.920
in the whole province.

00:42:41.920 --> 00:42:42.920
Thanks for bringing me.

00:42:43.710 --> 00:42:45.150
But will you let me pick up the tab?

00:42:45.840 --> 00:42:46.840
You're a girl.

00:42:47.190 --> 00:42:48.320
So what if I'm a girl?

00:42:48.760 --> 00:42:49.526
You took me for a ride,

00:42:49.550 --> 00:42:50.550
so I'm buying you dinner.

00:42:50.630 --> 00:42:51.630
It's only fair.

00:42:52.590 --> 00:42:53.110
Fair enough.

00:42:53.230 --> 00:42:54.910
I'll give the Vice Mayor some credit then.

00:42:56.360 --> 00:42:57.710
How do you know my dad?